reviewText: An interesting insight of the actor! Charlie Rose has really got the knack of being an interviewer. I wish I bought the dvd used.

I purchased this DVD from Amazon.com because it showed an interview with Benicio Del Toro.  I am an ardent fan of Mr. Del Toro & anything he's in, in my opinion, is worthwhile watching & listening too. I think he is a phenomenal actor, a great humanitarian & oh so gorgeous looking. I wish all of his interviews were on DVD's so I could purchase them from Amazon.com.
